{"id":"1477bd46-da44-445e-9f69-347912f9c1d2","title":"1548/08/10: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"18e113e2-914e-45e7-93b9-f20e1936a2fc","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, August 10th, 1548.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"02a9f7e4-87d4-4e5b-8e3c-0e068bccbe42","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"01c207d4-4524-47d4-8850-827409a996c8","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"9a561f6f-2893-401b-afd8-35531e99f054","type":"codex/time-reference","start":11,"end":27,"value":"75374c1f-d7a3-4a35-adaa-386079f3aa03","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"c6cae3d7-d3fb-4a98-b8c2-bc3e98e800a9","type":"style/superscript","start":20,"end":21,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"9c0b581d-1b85-46e2-88f5-a4684f9d71b8","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"eb8ee9a4-7ccf-43db-bc92-a1dbcbe545fe","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"b0e3e369-648c-4fcc-80b7-e0dcace5fc17","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b0db9d2b-86f1-400b-b93d-fbe7c0d026dc","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"114a0a96-ec5f-44f3-a4ea-1b55a824116f","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"384b0685-8d83-4dab-a53e-3b2b9b271169","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"b96e783f-0f3e-4ab4-9e79-4f63e03f9c73","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"78ab8e9b-e86d-419e-a8f1-b731e4e65240","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0Thou hast written to me saying ye have a farm under consideration valued at 1,300\u00A0florins, outside the Porta al Prato. If it be a good\u00A0thing I think ye ought to secure it at all costs,\u00A0provided there be no doubts as to the ownership and we be not involved in law-suits to follow. Have a care that it be not situated where the floods of the Arno can damage it. If thou shouldst hear of any\u00A0large property for sale, about ten or fifteen miles from\u00A0Florence,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I mean something costing about three or four thousand crowns\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I should like to buy it so that I could secure the revenue myself: for as I have lost the Porto I am now in the position of having to find a source of income that cannot be taken from me, and I would much rather that it were near Florence than\u00A0anywhere else. I have written to thee of this matter so that when thou hearest of some good thing that is going\u00A0for about the price I have mentioned thou mayest send me news of it quietly. There is nothing to add. Salute everybody in the house in my name, and commend me to Messer Giovan Francesco.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"c86a9b86-707c-4a29-9eb8-6b28760f077f","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5d0e0074-12ce-439c-ac4f-591edb1fe659","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"5fa97776-7a79-4f5c-ab82-40ff89a65453","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":12,"end":15,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"7e77ecf9-1075-42c9-80e6-0306ed08c80d","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":33,"end":34,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"4d75e144